Available commands:
1.Initialize shop with files.
savefiles&<client_file>&<product_file>&<category_file>

2.Server data view.
showpr
showcli
showcat

3.Show product from given product category.
getpc&<category_name>

4.Look for client in client database.
findcli&<client_email>

5.Get product price for client.
getprcli&<client_email>.<product_name>

6.Add object to database.
addcli&<name>&<surname>&<email>&<discount_level>
addprod&<price>&<name>&<category>&<amount>
addpc&<name>

7.Delete objects from database.
delCli&<client_name>
delPro&<product_name>
delProCat&<category_name> | Deletes products assigned to category as well.

8.Save database state.
save
